An Android app that lets you show the k-9 mail unread mails in a SAMSUNG phone with the standard launcher (TouchWiz).

To use this app you need:
* K-9 Mail [https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fsck.k9].
* A SAMSUNG phone with the standard launcher (TouchWiz).


Thanks to...
* the K-9 Mail team, for their great mail app.
* shafty023, for his SamsungBadger lib [https://github.com/shafty023/SamsungBadger].
* baolongnt, for some code in his EmailPopup addon [https://github.com/baolongnt/EmailPopup].
